  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, M</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra into a Chakra Storing Gem to start an overload, then throw it like a grenade with a 10 ft range increment (D20 Modern, p148), dealing 3d6 force damage (Reflex halves), and has an additional effect based on your primary elemental affinity:<br><br>- Earth: 1d6 earth damage, targets make a Fortitude save against being stunned 1 round.<br>- Fire: 3d6 fire damage, damages unattended objects and sets fire to combustible materials.<br>- Ice: 1d6 cold damage, targets make a Fortitude save against being unable to run or charge for 2 rounds.<br>- Lightning: 1d6 electric damage, targets make a Fortitude save against being deafened 1d6 rounds.<br>- Water: 2d6 water damage, douses small fires, damages paper and fragile fabrics, creates 10 liters of water.<br>- Wind: 2d6 wind damage, snuffs out small fires.</p>\n\n\n\n",
